# HALL SESSION ACTIVE

All external plugin skills are suppressed while a Hall session is open. Do not invoke skills from `superpowers` or any other plugin namespace. Use Hall commands instead.

| Need | Hall command |
|------|--------------|
| Brainstorm | Old Major inline (no command needed) |
| Plan | `/hall:plan` |
| Dispatch | `/hall:dispatch` |
| Review | `/hall:review` |
| Sync | `/hall:reconcile` |
